{
 "name": "RPlog_Return_to_Renaal_IV",
 "title": "Return to Renaal IV",
 "summary": "Over the backwater border world of Renaal IV, a small band of raiders -- the Z-95 Headhunter Cyclopean Rage, the RX4 patrol craft Diligence, and their wingmen -- ambush an Imperial supply convoy of freighters escorted by a light cruiser and a full Interceptor squadron led by Flight Officer Molokai. As the fast raider ships sweep in on the lumbering convoy, the Imperial TIE pilots, including the cocky Pilot Officer Ricoar, scramble to intercept. A swirling starfighter battle erupts around the convoy as raiders and Imperials trade fire over the contested space-lane.",
